
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home | Handyman Cruz">
  <BaseHead title="Home | Handyman Cruz" description="Modern handyman and technology-inspired service profile for Cruz." />

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-cyan-400/20 py-24">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_15%_20%,rgba(6,182,212,0.25),transparent_30%),radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_10%,rgba(37,99,235,0.3),transparent_35%),linear-gradient(120deg,#020617,#0f172a)]"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 text-center md:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-300">My Visual Résumé</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold md:text-6xl">A way for me to show off some of my technical & building skills.</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">Please feel free to look around and get to know who I am, what I offer, and why my work stands out above others..</p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/services" class="rounded-full bg-cyan-400 px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-cyan-300">Explore Services</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="rounded-full border border-cyan-200/40 px-6 py-3 font-semibold hover:bg-white/10">View Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-6 px-4 py-16 md:grid-cols-3 md:px-8">
    <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-300">Technology Enthusiast</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">If im not out and about, you'll tend to find me online.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-300">Gamer</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">In my spare time, I love to play a few games of Rocket League, Brawlhalla or Momentum Mod Playtest!</p>
    </article>
    <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-cyan-300">Hands On</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">I enjoy puling apart items or devices and attempting to fix them myself. Some call it fidgety, but I like to see it as mechanically minded.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
